Anonsurf will anonymize the entire system under TOR using IPTables. It will also allow you to start and stop i2p (Invisible Internet Project) as well



                 -------X-------                        -------X-------                        -------X-------
                                                            
                                                            **INSTALLING ANONSURF**

git clone https://github.com/Und3rf10w/kali-anonsurf.git

cd kali-anonsurf/

sudo ./installer.sh

sudo anonsurf start
[Starts anonsurf]

anonsurf status
[Check if deployment is successful]

anonsurf myip
[Displays allocated IP]

anonsurf change
[Allocates a new ip - restarting TOR services]

sudo anonsurf stop
[Stops anonsurf]
